    <h1>7-Day High-Protein Meal Plan for Men Over 50 <span>(Simple, Real Food)</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">No meal prep marathon. No exotic ingredients. Just real food hitting 120–140g of protein daily — distributed the right way.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem; font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--green-dark);">Most men aren't low on effort — they're just 40–60 grams short every day.</p>
