    <p>Each day is structured as breakfast / lunch / dinner / snack. Totals shown are approximate and assume average serving sizes. Adjust portions up or down based on your specific daily target.</p>

    <p><strong>Don't follow this perfectly — follow the pattern.</strong> The architecture matters more than hitting every meal exactly as written.</p>

